column5: With these warmer then norm temps,it,s going to be sometime before we,ll be doing this  Terry,remember this day   It wasnt that cold was it.    Terry,why are yer cheeks so red.     Who says there are no 15 inch perch      Ok this one isnt.LOL  Theres a memory.    Come on mother nature,stop this, and give up cold and snow.

ah yeah what was the temp that day -35 or something.. and look at how thick  the soles of my boots are they make me taller then Roy, when I am wearing them  and now with the aquavu camera I have/am getting for xmas, I will be haulling it the 15"ers

There should be some in there...  Cph and I threw all perch over 12 inches back in this fall...there were a couple over the 14 inch mark...  Twice I kept 4 in the 10 to 12 inch size for dinner for Maribeth and myself and all went back the other time...
finally I can say "I know that spot"...no church steeples or anything.
Bian,don,t worry it will be here soon enough bud,and can,t wait .  Steve
The church is just to the left Riz  Steve I hear ya bud.
